thrillers.title: Thrillers
thrillers.description: These heart-pounding mystery and suspense films will have you on the edge of your seat.

300169.title: The Ninth Gate
300169.description: A rare-book dealer acquires a demonic manuscript, leading to a series of terrifying supernatural occurrences as he uncovers the truth about the book.

300459.title: Not Without My Daughter
300459.description: In this thriller based on a true story, an Iranian-American man takes his American wife and daughter to visit Iran, only to keep them hostage there.

302505.title: The Substitute
302505.description: Undercover as a substitute teacher, an ex-marine cleans up the crime-infested school when he discovers a gang tormenting students and staff.

303190.title: The Usual Suspects
303190.description: The lone survivor of a heist-gone-wrong tells the feds how it all went down as they search for the enigmatic crime lord behind the disaster.

308307.title: Buried
308307.description: Paul Conroy wakes up buried six feet underground with a lighter, a rapidly dying cell phone, low oxygen and no idea who put him there or why.

312183.title: Jeepers Creepers
312183.description: After making a horrific discovery in the basement of an old church, a pair of siblings find themselves the chosen prey of an indestructible force.

312423.title: Out of Time
312423.description: Implicated in a suspicious fire, a small-town police chief must stay a step ahead of his own police force to solve a murder and prove his innocence.

316461.title: Hard Candy
316461.description: A 14-year-old girl turns the tables on her would-be predator in this psychological thriller.

358575.title: Mississippi Burning
358575.description: Based on the true story, two FBI agents investigate the disappearance of three Mississippi civil rights activists in 1964.

367706.title: Jailbait
367706.description: She killed her stepfather in self-defense. Now, Anna must fight her dark side and survive the world of girl gangs and predatory guards in juvy.

367819.title: Titanic 2
367819.description: A century after the fateful voyage of the original, modern luxury liner Titanic II sets sail. Will this ship suffer the same fate as her namesake?

385507.title: Empire State
385507.description: When two friends attempt to rob an armored car depository containing millions, they must elude a veteran NYPD detective and angry local crime bosses.

417725.title: Chained
417725.description: A serial-killer cabbie kidnaps a boy and makes him his servant. Years later, will the boy follow in his captor's footsteps or make his escape?

418820.title: Don't Hang Up
418820.description: An evening of drunken prank calls becomes a nightmare for a pair of teens when a mysterious stranger turns their game into something deadly.

436109.title: No One Lives
436109.description: A vicious, ruthless gang has no idea that they’ve just kidnapped a person who is determined to turn the tables on them, one by one.

448257.title: Amores Perros
448257.description: A horrific car accident connects the lives of three strangers: a lovesick dog fighter, an injured supermodel and a hitman running from his past.

448434.title: Bait
448434.description: When a freak tsunami traps people inside a supermarket, a pack of killer sharks let them know they aren’t the only ones who are shopping for dinner.

451668.title: Miss Meadows
451668.description: Miss Meadows is a just a prim school teacher on the outside but inside hides the soul of a vigilante, righting wrongs by whatever means necessary.

456902.title: Trust
456902.description: When an adolescent girl meets her first boyfriend online, he turns out to be a sexual predator who tears the life of her happy suburban family apart.

456923.title: The Iceman
456923.description: Based on a shocking true story, a family man goes to great lengths to keep his work as a ruthless hitman a secret from the people he loves.

460204.title: King of New York
460204.description: A New York drug lord just released from prison is determined to rule the streets again with a vengeance in this gritty action film.

465367.title: Bones
465367.description: 20 years after his death, a local legend and benefactor returns as a ghost to avenge those who killed him and restore his neighborhood.

466197.title: The Remains
466197.description: A family moves into an old Victorian home and finds a trunk in the attic filled with items tainted by an evil spirit hellbent on harming the children.

466704.title: Jamesy Boy
466704.description: The true story of a teen, who goes from a street gang to a maximum security prison, and the convicted murderer who helps him turn his life around.

469586.title: Hard Target
469586.description: The line between the hunted and the hunter becomes blurred when one man finds himself fighting a group that hunts other men for blood sport.

469821.title: Fear
469821.description: A teenage girl’s dream crush on an older man, whom even her family approves of, turns terrifying when he reveals he’s an obsessed, psychopath stalker.

472908.title: Odd Thomas
472908.description: In a small desert town, a fry cook with psychic gifts, his girlfriend, and the sheriff team up to stop a weird stranger from unleashing an evil force.

473357.title: Fatal Instinct
473357.description: The hunt for serial killer becomes personal for a police detective when the evidence leads him to an ex-con he put in prison years ago.

476644.title: The Boondock Saints
476644.description: Irish brothers try to clean up Boston’s underworld by knocking off gangsters and become local folk heroes, as an FBI agent traces their bloody trail.

477962.title: Set It Off
477962.description: Four African-American women in Los Angeles, all in dire financial circumstances, resort to robbing banks with action-packed, tragic consequences.

478806.title: Dark Was the Night
478806.description: After a logging company moves into a small town, a sheriff and his deputy uncover a new breed of terror which changes everything.

480194.title: Even Lambs Have Teeth
480194.description: After being abducted by a small town full of psychopaths, two beautiful young women take savage and imaginative revenge on their attackers.

488471.title: Kill or Be Killed
488471.description: In 1900, a vicious gang of cutthroat outlaws ride across Texas to recover a fortune in hidden loot in their most daring robbery yet.

491715.title: Hell House LLC
491715.description: Five years after the deadly opening night of a Halloween attraction, a documentary film crew investigates the haunted house where it all took place.

493084.title: Life on the Line
493084.description: With a huge storm barreling down on their hometown, a team of brave linemen risk it all to make sure essential services stay online.

493370.title: The Whole Truth
493370.description: A lawyer fights to clear a teen in the brutal stabbing of his father but, as more evidence comes to light, the whole truth is darker than he thought.

505984.title: Last Shift
505984.description: A rookie cop oversees the last shift at a closing police station, but soon discovers the building’s connection to a cult, and all hell breaks loose.

507459.title: Clown
507459.description: A father puts on an old clown suit to save his son’s birthday party. He soon finds that the suit, the wig, and the makeup cannot be taken off at all.

512252.title: We Need to Talk About Kevin
512252.description: In this suspenseful and gripping psychological thriller, a mother contends for years with the increasing malevolence of her first-born child, Kevin.

520255.title: Dark Skies
520255.description: An average family’s quiet suburban existence begins to unravel when a series of unexplained and terrifying events leave them to fend for themselves.

527970.title: Blitz
527970.description: A tough cop and his sidekick, who faces ridicule from their homophobic squad, are dispatched to take down a serial killer who targets the police.

528599.title: Takers
528599.description: High-octane thriller about a group of notorious criminals whose streak of untraceable bank heists may come to an end thanks to a hardcore detective.

528667.title: When the Bough Breaks
528667.description: The trust between a married couple and the woman carrying their child is torn when the surrogate decides she wants the husband and baby for herself.

539274.title: The Glass House
539274.description: When Ruby and her brother are orphaned after a family tragedy, they're taken in by family friends. Until it becomes clear that something is wrong.

543873.title: Desperado
543873.description: Stunning visuals highlight this action classic as a lone and mysterious gunman shoots through a border town to find his girlfriend’s killer.

553603.title: Stolen From the Suburbs
553603.description: When teenage Emma is drugged and abducted into a sex trafficking ring, her widowed single mother must pose as a customer in order to save her.

559448.title: En El Infierno (Doblado)
559448.description: Dentro de la prisión más corrupta de Europa del Este, un prisionero cumpliendo cadena perpetua se enfrenta a un alcaide en una lucha a muerte.

563036.title: Bad Company
563036.description: When his identical twin brother is killed in the line of duty, a streetwise punk is recruited by a CIA agent to stop an arms deal from going bad.

569508.title: Look Away
569508.description: A tormented teen tired of being bullied decides to switch places with her darker alter ego who lives in the mirror, to frightening results.

572750.title: The Blackout: Invasion Earth
572750.description: A military crew discovers an outpost of survivors surrounded by corpses, from cars to hospitals, and tries to find out the cause of the mass deaths.

579634.title: Warning Shot
579634.description: A single mom and her young child struggle to get by, until they inherit the family farmhouse, but a battle over water rights threatens their lives.

585035.title: Hard Target 2
585035.description: After accidentally killing his friend in a match, an MMA fighter self-exiles in Bangkok where a wealthy man tricks him into being hunted for sport.

589063.title: The Specialist
589063.description: An ex-CIA explosives expert with his own dark past helps a seductive beauty avenge the murder of her parents by a powerful Cuban-American crime boss.

591015.title: Proud Mary
591015.description: Taraji P. Henson stars as a steely hit woman working for a local Mob family who finds a protective instinct for a little boy while out for a kill.

591420.title: A Perfect Getaway
591420.description: A romantic Hawaiian vacation turns deadly for two pairs of lovers, when a duo of murderers begins targeting tourists who cannot escape the island.

591434.title: Trespass
591434.description: When two firemen discover a map leading to a fortune abandoned in a tenement, they become the targets of a vicious gang, led by a notorious mobster.

591447.title: Dragonfly
591447.description: A grieving pediatric doctor at a Chicago hospital wonders if his late, pregnant wife is contacting him through his patients' near-death experiences.

595451.title: Complex
595451.description: The disappearance of a woman and the murder of another leads to the investigation of four different families, living inside of one apartment complex.

595889.title: Introspectum Motel
595889.description: Two strangers head down a dark and twisted path inside themselves and confront their choices as they begin to uncover the connection between them.

599603.title: Contagion
599603.description: Oscar®-winning filmmaker Steven Soderbergh (Ocean's Eleven films, Traffic) returns to large-scale cinema with this global action thriller that revolves around the threat of a deadly outbreak of a fatal disease and the people determined to keep it at bay. As the fast-moving epidemic grows, the worldwide medical community races to find a cure and control the panic that spreads faster than the virus itself. At the same time, ordinary people struggle to survive in a society coming apart. A stellar international ensemble cast including Academy Award® winners Matt Damon, Gwyneth Paltrow, Kate Winslet, Marion Cotillard and nominees Jude Law and Laurence Fishburne portray the dedicated doctors at the CDC and World Health Organization who rush to contain the outbreak of a new virus. Tracking its source to Hong Kong and searching for a cure, these determined Samaritans do their utmost to limit deaths, civil unrest and the false rumors surrounding the disease in this viral outbreak drama with multiple plot lines in the style of Soderbergh's Oscar®-winning narcotics drama Traffic.

599629.title: Eyes Wide Shut
599629.description: Tom Cruise and Nicole Kidman star as a married couple entangled in an intricate web of jealousy and sexual obsession in Stanley Kubrick's final cinematic offering.  At a Christmas party hosted by wealthy, unconventional Victor Ziegler (Sydney Pollack), provocative advances and innocent flirtations arouse suspicion as high-society physician Dr. William Harford (Cruise) and his sexy wife, Alice (Kidman) watch each other from a distance. Alone later, this seemingly perfect couple confront their intimate sexual fantasies--which don't include each other.  Caught between reality and illusion, jealousy and obsession, William struggles with his inner urges. Will he act on his erotic fantasies or keep them hidden deep inside? Sometimes a man can see more clearly with his Eyes Wide Shut.

600021.title: Striptease
600021.description: For her most daring role ever, Demi Moore bares all in this erotic satire about a single mother who turns to stripping in a Miami nightclub to earn money for a child-custody battle. But her sensual dancing attracts the unwanted attention of a deranged congressman who will stop at nothing--even murder--to possess her.

602292.title: Blade
602292.description: A vampire-human hybrid uses his advanced powers and an arsenal of weapons to do battle with the bloodsucking monsters who threaten the living.

607952.title: True Lies
607952.description: A deadly and talented spy for the government hides his dangerous day job from his family, but his secret heroics take a toll on his marriage.

609342.title: When Love Kills: The Falicia Blakely Story
609342.description: Looking for a better life for her new baby, 16-year-old Falicia is led down a path of violent crime after taking a job as an exotic dancer.

612777.title: The Kitchen
612777.description: Set in 1978 Hell's Kitchen, this is the story of three housewives whose mobster husbands are sent to prison, leaving them to handle business.

613766.title: Swim
613766.description: After a storm floods a family’s vacation rental home, they must get past a vicious shark that has found its way inside the house.

620779.title: Siberia
620779.description: After an American diamond merchant and his lover fall into a bad business deal in Russia, they must evade crossfire between the buyer and Feds.

620886.title: The Road
620886.description: Following an apocalyptic event, a father and son travel through North America’s dangerous terrain in the hopes of reaching the ocean.

621292.title: Black Dog
621292.description: An ex-convict truck driver with makes one last no-questions-asked trip, only to discover that his rig is stocked with assault weapons.

622282.title: The Invitation
622282.description: Will accepts an invitation to a dinner party hosted by his ex-wife and her new husband and begins to suspect an ambush when the affair goes awry.

624826.title: Martyrs
624826.description: Fifteen years after escaping her captors in an abandoned slaughterhouse, Lucie’s revenge plot takes her on a terrifying journey of her own depravity.

626043.title: Civil Brand
626043.description: This film, whose title is a play on the former Sybil Brand prison for women in California, is about 4 jailed women fighting corruption on the inside.

630921.title: The Last House on the Left
630921.description: After their daughter is raped and left for dead, a couple exact bloody revenge on the attackers who have unknowingly taken shelter at their home.

631544.title: Monsters of Man
631544.description: An illegal U.S. military op goes awry when killer robots are unleashed on heroin producers in Southeast Asia and end up wiping out an entire village.

635480.title: In Broad Daylight
635480.description: When Malik learns his cousin has been kidnapped and is being held hostage by her obsessive ex-boyfriend, he becomes a one-man search army to find her.

637106.title: Unknown
637106.description: A man awakens from a coma after a car wreck to find his wife doesn’t recognize him, his identity has been stolen, and hitmen are trying to kill him.

637929.title: Carlito's Way
637929.description: In 1975 NYC, a rehabilitated ex-con drug dealer determined to stay clean is tempted back into the life by an array of lowlifes and former associates.

638331.title: Cowboys & Aliens
638331.description: “Iron Man” director Jon Favreau directed this sci-fi Western with Daniel Craig and Harrison Ford squaring off against a massive intergalactic threat.

639782.title: Ninja Assassin
639782.description: After a trained ninja leaves behind his former life, he works with a Europol agent to take down the hired killers who taught him everything he knows.

642282.title: Escape Room
642282.description: When three couples celebrate a 30th birthday with an escape room, they quickly realize that the game is deadly, and only winners survive.

645268.title: The Hit List
645268.description: It’s a high-octane race against death when a man meets a hit man in a bar who makes him an offer to kill any five people he wants out of his life.

645956.title: Risen
645956.description: A terrifying end of days scenario threatens life and safety as we know it after a meteorite explosion contaminates an Australian farming town.

646030.title: Striking Distance
646030.description: Bruce Willis and Sarah Jessica Parker star in this crime thriller about a demoted homicide cop who works with his partner to find his father’s killer.

646376.title: The Girl Who Got Away
646376.description: Twenty years after her conviction, a serial child-killer escapes from prison, to go after the one intended victim who got away and finish the job.

650036.title: Dirty Work
650036.description: A young fashion graduate becomes a personal assistant for an over-the-top erotic novelist, starting an affair that gets her drawn into a murder plot.

651120.title: The Tourist
651120.description: An American tourist visiting Italy to mend a broken heart is seduced by a beautiful woman, who ensnares him in an international criminal plot.

651461.title: A Mother's Rage
651461.description: Lori Laughlin stars as a mother driving her daughter to her new college who ferociously fights off a psychotic person terrorizing them on the highway.

652267.title: Deception
652267.description: A happily married woman watches her life fall apart after she learns that her lawyer husband is having an affair with his assistant.

655371.title: Project Gemini
655371.description: Centuries of destroying Earth’s resources leaves humankind’s last chance at survival in space where an unimaginable force is lying in wait.

657674.title: The Edge
657674.description: A plane crash in the Alaskan wilderness pits two enemies and a billionaire against a blood-thirsty Kodiak bear in a brutal struggle for survival.

657981.title: Trust Nobody
657981.description: A young hustler's untamed thirst for power can make him destroy his own family while a woman's greed can cause her to do the unthinkable.

663440.title: Dead Man Down
663440.description: A hitman for a New York crime lord is seduced and blackmailed by a victim seeking retribution who leads him on a violent and cathartic revenge spree.

665895.title: Corrective Measures
665895.description: As tensions rise among supervillain inmates and corrupt staff, the march toward anarchy begins in the world’s most dangerous maximum-security prison.

671643.title: Shattered
671643.description: A stroke of fate introduces a millionaire divorcé to a mysterious woman he quickly falls for, but will soon come to suspect of dangerous motives.

673630.title: Daughter of the Wolf
673630.description: After her son gets kidnapped, an ex-military specialist, instead of seeking help, captures one of the kidnappers and uses him to track down her son.

674424.title: The Stepmother
674424.description: After a recently widowed single father moves to a new town, a new mysterious woman threatens his relationship with his son and their safety.

676316.title: Chica Perdida: Una Historia De Hollywood (Doblado)
676316.description: Las historias de cuatro mujeres involucradas en la industria del sexo se entrelazan, ofreciendo un vistazo al lado más oscuro de Los Ángeles.

676700.title: Nude Nuns With Big Guns
676700.description: Packing heat and taking no prisoners, a young nun strikes back against the men who made her life a living hell in this outrageous modern cult classic.

679437.title: Shark Bait
679437.description: A group of friends race stolen jet skis out to sea, ending up in a head on collision without means to get home when they realize they’re not alone in predator-infested water.

680196.title: Dangerous
680196.description: A reformed sociopath travels to a remote island to uncover the truth behind his brother’s mysterious death, but he's met by a band of mercenaries.

682043.title: A Score to Settle
682043.description: With only a short time to live, Frankie Carver is released from prison, vowing to track down every last member of the gang that betrayed him.

684103.title: The Lost Tribe
684103.description: Shipwrecked on a remote island, a group of friends discover they are being hunted by a tribe of monstrous, flesh-eating evolutionary throwbacks.

684117.title: Would You Rather
684117.description: In this darkly comic thriller, the sadistic host of a party forces his guests to turn on each other and play a lethal game of Would You Rather.

684126.title: The Stanford Prison Experiment
684126.description: Based on the infamous true story, two dozen students role play as prisoners and guards in a terrifying experiment that shocked the world.

684138.title: The House That Jack Built
684138.description: An architect-turned-serial killer who views murder as art recounts his "life's work" in this audacious film from visionary Lars von Trier.

684884.title: Don't Breathe
684884.description: A group of teens breaks into a blind man's home, thinking they'll get away with the perfect crime but get more than they bargained for once inside.

687954.title: Pulpit Gangster
687954.description: Pastor Arthur Allen Jr. of Atlanta’s infamous House of Prayer takes his years of manipulation, gambling and street hustling to the pulpit.

688604.title: Dad Crush
688604.description: After transferring to a new school where her father teaches English, Riley befriends a student who develops a dangerous obsession with her dad.

692126.title: True to the Game 2
692126.description: Based on a NY Times Best Seller, this film picks up a year after the first film and follows the lives of the characters affected by Quadir’s murder.

694827.title: Accident
694827.description: A group of teenagers suffers a terrible accident during a joy ride but getting trapped at the bottom of a ravine becomes the least of their worries.

698128.title: Running With the Devil
698128.description: A tenacious federal agent traces the supply line of a ring of experienced cocaine dealers, as two cartel envoys hunt for a shipment lost in transit.

698742.title: Bed Rest
698742.description: After struggling to start a family, Julie Rivers is pregnant again. Put on mandatory bed rest, Julie starts unraveling as ghostly experiences in the home begin closing in on her.

698959.title: Repo Men
698959.description: After being outfitted with a top-of-the-line heart replacement, an organ repo man must go on the run when he finds himself unable to pay for it.

698965.title: The Jackal
698965.description: An engaging suspense thriller about a ruthless assassin hired to eliminate a powerful, high-ranking official in the U.S. government.

698980.title: Dead Silence
698980.description: After the murder of his wife, a man returns to his hometown and uncovers the terrifying legend of Mary Shaw, a cursed ventriloquist from the 40s.

698981.title: Drag Me to Hell
698981.description: When loan officer Christine decides to evict an older woman, she becomes the victim of an evil spirit determined to drag her to hell.

698985.title: The Signal
698985.description: In this sci-fi thriller, three students encounter a mysterious signal in the desert and find themselves at the mercy of a man in a hazmat suit.

701398.title: The Minute You Wake Up Dead
701398.description: In this noir thriller, a stockbroker romances a waitress as multiple murders shock a small Southern town. Someone’s getting rich. But who?

701400.title: Detective Knight: Rogue
701400.description: While chasing bandits from Los Angeles to New York, detective James Knight crashes into his dark past, imperiling his case—and his life.

702155.title: No Escape
702155.description: An online influencer and his friends enter a battle for survival in Moscow’s world of excess and danger where reality and social media are blurred.

702672.title: Vacaciones De Terror
702672.description: Una familia adinerada hereda una casa vacacional que se encuentra embrujada por el espíritu de una bruja que fue quemada en la hoguera.

705428.title: Yenni Thuniga
705428.description: After his fiancé is accidentally killed in a jewel heist gone wrong, a man seeks revenge on the gang responsible.

705436.title: Prisoner of Love
705436.description: Inspired by a true story. A corrections officer falls in love with an inmate and helps plot his escape, leaving her hometown to question her choices.

705468.title: Gaslight
705468.description: After her inheritance begins to disappear, Brooke is unsure if her husband is plotting to steal her money, or if she's starting to lose her mind.

708103.title: Wire Room
708103.description: During surveillance, a federal agent witnesses a hit squad murder a surveillance target and soon finds himself in their crosshairs.

708341.title: #Float
708341.description: Things turn deadly for Kali and her friends at the annual river float, as a sinister paranormal force plunges them into a life or death struggle.

708829.title: The Stepmother 2
708829.description: Elizabeth breaks free from the hospital with a new mission - find a new family and live happily ever after, she can’t escape her past and will fight.

710212.title: You're Not Alone
710212.description: An evil entity begins to torment a mother and daughter, forcing them to face the inexplicable presence that inhabits the walls of their new home.

710225.title: The Assistant
710225.description: Raven hires a new personal assistant, thinking she's found the perfect fit. But fear sets in when personal organization turns to personal obsession.

713119.title: Alarmed
713119.description: When a couple plans a getaway, things go terribly wrong when their son is held hostage in their high tech home and the only way to save him is to kill or be killed.

713221.title: Safe Word
713221.description: When a newlywed couple decides to open their relationship to strangers, the wife quickly realizes her husband is a sadistic monster whose fetishes might destroy her.

713911.title: Homewrecker
713911.description: A married couple decides to rent out the extra room in their house to an attractive young woman who moves in armed with a set of filthy schemes.

717197.title: True to the Game
717197.description: After falling for a young woman, a charismatic drug lord tries to leave his fast-paced and dangerous lifestyle behind to start a new life.

720949.title: Meeting Evil
720949.description: A man meets a stranger in need of his help, but he finds himself trying to protect his family when the guy turns out to represent unspeakable evil.

720951.title: Out for a Kill
720951.description: A professor becomes an unwitting accomplice in a foiled Mexican cocaine deal and must escape prison to prove his innocence and take his revenge.

720990.title: Til Death Do Us Part
720990.description: When her husband becomes abusive, Madison flees by faking her death and changing her identity. But she soon learns there's no escaping this nightmare.

722979.title: Best Friend
722979.description: Trisha and Jamie have been best friends since grade school. Jamie tries to keep Trisha’s new love interest apart, even if it costs someone’s life.

723256.title: Red Sparrow
723256.description: A Russian intelligence officer tasked with seducing a CIA agent finds her mission and its objective threatened when they both fall for each other.

723505.title: The Ladykillers
723505.description: An eccentric Southern professor and his crew pose as a band in order to rob a casino, all under the nose of his unsuspecting landlord.

724306.title: Devil's Knot
724306.description: The rural Arkansas town of West Memphis makes national headlines when three teenagers are arrested for the brutal murders of three young boys.

724340.title: The Autopsy of Jane Doe
724340.description: Coroners are mystified by an unidentified corpse until a series of terrifying events makes it clear that cadaver Jane Doe is not actually dead.

724344.title: You're Not Alone
724344.description: 30,000 ft in the air, Keith Mitchell (Michael Jai White) helplessly watches a stranger enter his home. There’s only one problem; his daughter is there.

724634.title: ATM
724634.description: A late-night stop at an ATM becomes a desperate fight for survival when three co-workers are trapped and terrorized by a mysterious hooded assailant.

724735.title: True to the Game 3
724735.description: Gena wakes to find Quadir is her savior and has just 72 hrs to return to Philly to let Bria and Gah Git know her plans, before her happily ever after.

725954.title: Always and Forever
725954.description: When Nicole's childhood friends start dying from alleged suicides, she suspects their deaths are linked to a grave mistake they made in middle school.

726033.title: Adulterers
726033.description: A man's fury is awakened when he returns home from work early to find his wife cheating on their wedding anniversary.

100000104.title: Gun
100000104.description: A new parolee reunites with his former criminal comrade and ignites a full-scale war with Detroit police to defend their business of gun-running.

100000105.title: The Housemaid
100000105.description: In this suspenseful, erotic thriller, a scandalous affair between a beautiful young maid and her wealthy employer has shocking consequences.

100000301.title: Castaways
100000301.description: In a post apocalyptic world, two women find themselves shipwrecked on a deserted island. As they fight to survive, the experience bonds them in ways they could never have imagined.

100000320.title: Taken 2
100000320.description: When retired CIA operative Brian Mills and his wife are taken hostage by a vengeful gang leader, they must rely on their daughter's help to escape.

100000371.title: The Threat Next Door
100000371.description: When an overworked single mother hires a friendly neighbor to babysit her daughter, she begins to face increasingly strange and threatening situations.

100000379.title: Classmates
100000379.description: A computer mixup gives two college freshman the chance to swap places but things take a turn when the switch puts them both in danger.

100000719.title: Surprise
100000719.description: Convinced his wife is cheating on him with his best friend, a husband goes off the deep end into a conspiracy, only to find himself unprepared for what comes next.

100000853.title: A Lonely Place to Die
100000853.description: Five climbers in the Scottish Highlands are thrust into a violent fight for their lives when they discover a girl who has been buried alive.

100000947.title: He's for the Streets
100000947.description: A successful man with everything Los Angeles has to offer plays the wrong woman, and she ends up taking everything he has worked so hard for.

100000965.title: A Good Man
100000965.description: Struggling in the aftermath of his wife's affair, a man's attempt at a new relationship begins to spiral out of control when he notices familiar signs.
